        <obo:IAO_0000115>A methyl benzene that is 1,3-dimethylbenzene which is substituted by a 5,6-dihydro-4&lt;em&gt;H&lt;/em&gt;-1,3-thiazin-2-ylnitrilo group at position 2. It is an α2 adrenergic receptor agonist and frequently used in veterinary medicine as an emetic and sedative with analgesic and muscle relaxant properties.</obo:IAO_0000115>
